{"tid":860842,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"認唔認同淺水灣沙灘好正旅遊景點？","createTime":"2018-10-13T15:51:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-14T03:02:24.000Z","uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ecff6d19ce8318f79d1c09928f18f60a83219837","tid":860842,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T15:51:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/13/234113_affa22f6aad9638562bccb678023497e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F13%2F234113_affa22f6aad9638562bccb678023497e.png&h=92610794&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/13/234114_6d9f0c62885637eebe828ae34ff710f3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F13%2F234114_6d9f0c62885637eebe828ae34ff710f3.png&h=f0162f3b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/13/234115_c0f3918427fe4bdf6ebad69c0226100e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F13%2F234115_c0f3918427fe4bdf6ebad69c0226100e.png&h=37c22413&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/13/234119_2934218abe99176ed2885fb2d6170b30.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F13%2F234119_2934218abe99176ed2885fb2d6170b30.png&h=5317f3f9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/13/234120_1f7b1d808b396cdc2f16bb7eeedf584d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F13%2F234120_1f7b1d808b396cdc2f16bb7eeedf584d.png&h=69d8b1f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n景靚<br />\n交通方便（我今日由金鐘坐巴士去只用咗二十分鐘,另外銅鑼灣亦有小巴入去）<br />\n同埋可以早啲落車，由深水灣沙灘沿著海邊漫步去淺水灣沙灘，沿途欣賞風景吹下海風<br />\n同埋淺水灣都有好多餐廳可以選擇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/13/235114_00335faab